    "directions": [
      "Mix all ingredients in stand mixer with hook for 9-12 min",
      "Dough should be elastic and smooth",
      "Shape into a ball using a wet cloth and proof for 1 hr",
      "When 1.5-2 times size re-knead until smooth; Divide into 8 portions",
      "Knead each portion for 1-2 min until smooth then roll out into an oval shape (ie: using a rolling pin)",
      "Slightly dust the oval (or brush lightly with oil) and folder over in half",
      "Place in steamer for 2-3 min; Then turn off heat and wait 15 min",
      "Restart heat and steam for 10 min after water begins to boil again"
