    "directions": [
      "Combine flour and salt",
      "Combine ~1 C / 200 g warm water, oil and yeast in a bowl",
      "Combine wet and dry; Knead until combined (~3 min); Rest 15 min",
      "Add flour and stir until mixture starts to come away from sides of the bowl (add more flour if needed)",
